snippet.title: Kira Kira Pop Princess: Cool new trailer!
snippet.description:
Learn cool new dance moves, buy clothes and style your character, Gaby, in this new cool game! 

Here is a sneak peek at the brand new dancing, music and fashion DS game 'Kira Kira Pop Princess' which is out on the Nintendo DS from the 7th March.
